	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Could the &quot;pixel aspect ratio&quot; option please have 4:3 added?  <br /><br />The currently available &quot;possible values&quot;: 1:1, 5:4, 8:7, 11:8, provides a close match with 5:4, with the effect of providing a picture aspect ratio of 5:4. That image is slightly too square though, matching the end results of a very old NTSC CRT from the 1950's.  <br /><br />NTSC CRT in later decades [1970/80/90's, 2000's], are 4:3 picture aspect ratio, slightly less square than the aforementioned 5:4 option's provisioning.  [5:4 = 1.25:1 &amp; 4:3 = 1.33:1]<br /><br />Thank You.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
